{"tid":1001516,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"容祖兒親認單身！情斷劉浩龍「好久了」","createTime":"2019-01-30T08:14:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T09:42:58.000Z","uid":3189,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"be4adb610bae9cc650e4dae44c9b8d44ea329494","tid":1001516,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:14:19.000Z","msg":"38歲容祖兒與42歲師兄劉浩龍去年3月傳出結束5年戀情，儘管男方否認分手，她卻一直未正面回應，昨晚出席活動時，拖磨10個月終於鬆口承認已分手，且已經有一段時間。<br />\n<br />\n容祖兒透露今年8月將和阿Sa、林鎧鈴等姊妹淘到希臘旅行，被問到劉浩龍會不會隨行？她直接說：「沒有！沒有好久了！作為藝人，我的每個發言和聲明對任何人都有影響，感情事是想低調處理，但問到我，我就誠實和大家說，我現在是單身。」<br />\n<br />\n傳2人是因外界及長輩壓力，加上雙方未來規劃不同而情變，容祖兒2012年與劉浩龍交往時，雙方名氣差距過大，屢被唱衰戀情，被爆分手還被指是為劉浩龍演唱會造勢，現在自己揭曉謎底，真的和師兄說掰掰。（郭妤／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190130/1509856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190130%2F1509856%2F&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfBz44BXU%2FO%2BPkTPvsbUsuc1I%3D&h=d09c43d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190130%2F1509856%2F&h=d3a16c96\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190130/1509856/</a>"},{"pid":"5eafcca705ee0e4cae0b9943437e3fc28f25bfe9","tid":1001516,"uid":12469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:14:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe395d6e0213ba61a77757cd8f577b4a83c23e4","tid":1001516,"uid":184108,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T08:53:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a8b355eb24b47b03dffcf5b39b3722c4c426c30f","tid":1001516,"uid":177727,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"根本係Les<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7427a57292f6ec66541cdb718a1cdef7c294cb70","tid":1001516,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi